title: Tsugai ni Narenai!
sinopse:
After reuniting with his first love and childhood friend Satoshi, the innocent and air-headed Ritsu sets out on a mission of a lifetime: he must now play the part of an ultra experienced and perverted omega to seduce his childhood friend! An erotic college rom-com omegaverse.

(Source: xiaojiangworld)

Included one-shot: Unmei no Tsugai, Sonna Mono wa Nai.
